project_descr: Today in Ethiopia, climate change considerations are not reflected in development planning and decision making at national and local level. The expected changes in climate and its impact on livelihoods are severe in the highlands of Ethiopia.

outputs.output_descr: If climate change is not addressed it is more than likely that expected development gains will not be realized. The impacts of weather variability and CC will not be uniform: some regions are more vulnerable than others.

document_name: Implementing CRGE in highlind areas in Ethiopia
project_title: implementing crge in highlind areas in ethiopia
